<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Decision Matrix Home Page</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #f5f5f5;
			color: #333;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		.container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
			height: 100vh;
			overflow: hidden;
			position: relative;
		}

		.background {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			height: 100%;
			width: 100%;
			background-image: url('fork-in-the-road.jpg');
			background-size: cover;
			background-position: center;
			animation: slide 60s linear infinite;
		}

		@keyframes slide {
			from { transform: translateX(0); }
			to { transform: translateX(-100%); }
		}

		.header {
			background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			color: #333;
			padding: 20px;
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 2em;
			margin: 0;
			width: 100%;
			box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		}

		h1 {
			margin: 0;
		}

		.intro {
			margin: 20px auto;
			max-width: 800px;
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 1.2em;
			line-height: 1.5;
			padding: 20px;
			background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
			border-radius: 10px;
			box-shadow: 0px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			animation: pop 0.3s ease;
		}

		.intro img {
			max-width: 100%;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			box-shadow: 0px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		.btn {
			display: inline-block;
			background-color: #333;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			text-decoration: none;
			margin-top: 20px;
			font-size: 1.2em;
			transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
			box-shadow: 0px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

		.btn:hover {
			background-color: #555;
		}

		.quote {
			font-style: italic;
			font-size: 1.5em;
			margin-top: 50px;
			margin-bottom: 0;
			text-align: center;
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {

			.intro {
				margin: 20px;
				font-size: 1em;
				padding: 10px;
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: 1.5em;
			}

			.btn {
        font-size: 1em;
			  padding: 10px 15px;
			  margin-top: 10px;
		  }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="background"></div>
		<div class="header">
			<h1>Stuck at a fork in the road?</h1>
			<p>Let our Decision Matrix guide you to the right path.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="intro">
			<img src="fork-in-the-road.jpg" alt="Fork in the road" />
			<p>Do you find yourself struggling to make a decision? Perhaps you're not sure which path to take or which factors to consider?</p>
			<p>Our Decision Matrix is here to help. By breaking down your options into a simple, easy-to-understand format, we'll help you navigate even the toughest decisions.</p>
			<a href="decision-matrix.html" class="btn">Go to Decision Matrix</a>
		</div>
		<p class="quote">"The hardest thing in life is to know which bridge to cross and which to burn."</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
